OL,3,CBank of England reveals which animals
OL,4,Ccould feature on its new-look banknotes
OL,6,FA dolphin, a fox, a butterfly, an owl,
OL,7,Fa bumblebee and a shark are among the
OL,8,Fanimals that could appear on Bank of
OL,9,FEngland banknotes, eventually
OL,10,Freplacing historical figures.
OL,12,FThe Bank of England wants people to
OL,13,Fgive their views on a selection of
OL,14,Fwildlife, native to the UK, that will
OL,15,Fappear on the next series of
OL,16,Fbanknotes, in a consultation launched
OL,17,Fon Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
