OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780448626
OL,3,CBank of England reveals which animals
OL,4,Ccould feature on its new-look banknotes
OL,6,FWorking with a panel of wildlife
OL,7,Fexperts, the Bank has produced a
OL,8,Fshortlist of animals that could become
OL,9,Fthe central image on the #5, #10, #20
OL,10,Fand #50 notes.
OL,12,FThe list has been grouped into three
OL,13,Fcategories, covering a variety of
OL,14,Fspecies and environments.
OL,16,FEach banknote will feature a different
OL,17,Fanimal. People are being asked to
OL,18,Fselect up to two examples from each
OL,19,Fcategory in the consultation, which
OL,20,Fruns until 11.59pm on July 3.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780448626
OL,3,CBank of England reveals which animals
OL,4,Ccould feature on its new-look banknotes
OL,6,FThe Bank said that only the animals on
OL,7,Fthe shortlist can feature as the
OL,8,Fcentral images on the new series and
OL,9,Fit is not seeking alternative
OL,10,Fnominations.
OL,12,FThe Bank said in July last year that
OL,13,Fwork would start on designing the next
OL,14,Fseries of banknotes, with a goal of
OL,15,Fincreasing counterfeit resilience.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780448626
OL,3,CBank of England reveals which animals
OL,4,Ccould feature on its new-look banknotes
OL,6,FIn March 2026, the Bank announced that
OL,7,Fnature had been chosen as the theme
OL,8,Ffor the next series of banknotes. The
OL,9,Ftopic received the highest proportion
OL,10,Fof nominations in last year's
OL,11,Fconsultation, as well as support in
OL,12,Ffocus groups.
OL,14,FMuch of the feedback received by the
OL,15,FBank referred to wildlife that is
OL,16,Fnative to the UK.
OL,18,FIt said that each banknote
OL,19,Fdenomination will need to be easy to
OL,20,Ftell apart.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780448626
OL,3,CBank of England reveals which animals
OL,4,Ccould feature on its new-look banknotes
OL,6,FIt is important that there are four
OL,7,Fdistinct animals across the four
OL,8,Fdenominations and that they are able
OL,9,Fto represent different environments
OL,10,Ffrom across the UK, the Bank said.
OL,12,FGiven this, the Bank said it may not
OL,13,Fnecessarily choose the four animals
OL,14,Fthat receive the highest number of
OL,15,Fresponses.
OL,17,FThe central images will also feature
OL,18,Fadditional elements from wildlife and
OL,19,Fnature.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780448626
OL,3,CBank of England reveals which animals
OL,4,Ccould feature on its new-look banknotes
OL,6,FBank of England Governor Andrew Bailey
OL,7,Fwill make the final decision, taking
OL,8,Finto account feedback from the public.
OL,10,FThe Bank said it wants to hear views
OL,11,Fin particular from residents of the UK
OL,12,Fand British citizens living abroad.
OL,13,FThey can be submitted via the Bank's
OL,14,Fwebsite or by post.
OL,16,FThe Bank will announce the outcome of
OL,17,Fits consultation by the end of 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780448626
OL,3,CBank of England reveals which animals
OL,4,Ccould feature on its new-look banknotes
OL,6,FIt will be a number of years before
OL,7,Fthe next series is launched, with a
OL,8,Fdetailed, multi-year process needed to
OL,9,Fdesign, test and print the banknotes,
OL,10,Fthe Bank said.
OL,12,FThis will help ensure they are
OL,13,Fresilient, accessible and include the
OL,14,Flatest anti-counterfeiting technology.
OL,16,FVictoria Cleland, Bank of England
OL,17,Fchief cashier, said: "I very much hope
OL,18,Fthe public will enjoy engaging in our
OL,19,Fconsultation to choose the animals to
OL,20,Ffeature on our next series of
OL,21,Fbanknotes.
OL,26,@yD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780448626
OL,3,CBank of England reveals which animals
OL,4,Ccould feature on its new-look banknotes
OL,6,F"The shortlisted animals demonstrate
OL,7,Fthe rich variety of wildlife we have
OL,8,Fto celebrate in the UK."
OL,10,FPeople will continue to see a human
OL,11,Fface as they take banknotes out of
OL,12,Ftheir wallets, even when animals are
OL,13,Fintroduced into designs, as the next
OL,14,Fseries will continue to include a
OL,15,Fportrait of the monarch.
OL,17,FRepresentation of the home nations
OL,18,Fwill also be an important feature in
OL,19,Fthe design, the Bank said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
