OL,3,CBank of England reveals which animals
OL,4,Ccould feature on its new-look banknotes
OL,6,FHistorical figures who have helped
OL,7,Fshape thought, innovation, leadership
OL,8,Fand values have been showcased on Bank
OL,9,Fof England banknotes since 1970.
OL,11,FThe first of the current series has
OL,12,Fbeen in circulation since 2016, when
OL,13,F#5 banknotes featuring Sir Winston
OL,14,FChurchill were issued.
OL,16,FThe current series of banknotes in
OL,17,Fcirculation also feature Jane Austen
OL,18,Fon the #10 banknote, JMW Turner on the
OL,19,F#20 and Alan Turing on the #50.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
