OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780448626
OL,3,CBank of England reveals which animals
OL,4,Ccould feature on its new-look banknotes
OL,6,FThe rise in payments technology such
OL,7,Fas contactless and mobile wallets has
OL,8,Fgiven people an increasing array of
OL,9,Falternatives to banknotes and coins.
OL,11,FCash remains the preferred payment
OL,12,Fmethod for about one in seven people
OL,13,Fand is used by many more, the Bank
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FIt said the amount of cash in
OL,17,Fcirculation has also continued to
OL,18,Fincrease, reaching #91.5 billion at
OL,19,Fthe end of February 2026.
OL,21,FBottlenose dolphin
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
